{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_20071.jpg","bgm":"bgm01_anime03","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"So, what should we do next...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"How about Torte joins us for the investigation?"},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"Yes, it's better than leaving her alone like this..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":100,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Yay!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20081.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":830300,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":830300}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_20081.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":101,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810000,"pos":2,"posX":50}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"[se:7222_happy]Oh, there they are...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"This world is inside their minds!"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"You can tell?"},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":101}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"[se:7222_happy]Yes, look!"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"It's just like with Kagome,@my hair reacted the same way!"},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Let's go talk to them!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"But...isn't it strange? It was just one book,@shouldn't it be a single person...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"It's not like that."},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"In this book, memories of multiple people seem to@have merged, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"We need to be careful not to make contact."},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"They call them Highway Robbers...the soldiers who@turned into marauding bands are increasing..."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830300,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story06","chara":[{"id":830300}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"... Jeanne La Pucelle? Who's that?","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Don't you remember...?@She liberated Orleans,"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"and guided Charles' coronation@in Reims as La Pucelle..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":830400,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"The situation in Orleans,@which was surrounded by England,"},{"chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"was rebuilt and led to liberation by Bâtard@and La Hire,"},{"chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"and the overall commander for the march to Reims@was Duke d'Alençon, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":830300,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"I heard that the reinforcement from Richemont@during the journey was significant."},{"chara":[{"id":830300}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"And during Charles' coronation,"},{"chara":[{"id":830300}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Gilles de Rais played the important role of offering@the holy oil."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":830400},{"effect":"fadeout","id":830300}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_20081.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"All of them are La Pucelle's comrades who fought@alongside her."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"From people's memories, only the existence of@La Pucelle is missing..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001},{"effect":"fadeout","id":402901}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":830300,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Thanks to Marshal Richemont's loyalty to King@Charles,"},{"chara":[{"id":830300}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"the court has been seized,"},{"chara":[{"id":830300}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"and since the Treaty of Arras five years ago,"},{"chara":[{"id":830300}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"England's influence has been significantly reduced..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":830300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"However, France is still in turmoil due to the@infighting among the nobles."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Opposing Marshal Richemont's methods,"},{"chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Duke d'Alençon and Bâtard are@clashing with King Charles..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"It resulted in public order being in disarray."},{"chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Instead of driving out England,@the French are killing each other."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_20081.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":100,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"Former comrades of La Pucelle are now enemies..."},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"This is what is happening after her death."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"That's..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":100,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Hey, soldiers... Can you really not remember?"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"The girl who looks just like me!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830300,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"You look like the lady...?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":831303}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"nameCenter":"Torte","textCenter":"Yes!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":830300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Hey, don't get so close to me..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"flashEffect":"flashWhiteSlow2","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830300,"lipSynch":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"[chara:830300:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]...?!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":831303},{"effect":"fadeout","id":830300}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830300,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"What's wrong?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"flashEffect":"flashWhiteSlow2","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"id":830300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"...!"},{"chara":[{"id":830300}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"Hey...!"},{"chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Ah...I remembered...!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/51015_singleraid_tart/memoria_1174.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"whiteIn","turnChangeInTime":1.0,"turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story07","nameNarration":"","narration":"YEAAAHHH!","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30.0,"narrationLineMargin":60.0,"narrationLineSpace":20.0,"turnChangeOut":"whiteOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.0},{"narration":"Orléans is free at last!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20091.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402101,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":402101}],"nameRight":"Tart","textRight":"Gentle Dauphin!","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":402101}],"nameRight":"Tart","textRight":"I have just come from Orleans...@And I am pleased to report that the French Army―"},{"bg":"bg_adv_20091.jpg","chara":[{"id":830200,"pos":1}],"nameNarration":"","narration":"*Clasp*","narrationBg":"bg_adv_20091.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"shake","face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402101,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"Tart","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"[chara:402101:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]...?!"},{"chara":[{"id":830200}],"nameCenter":"Dauphin Charles","textCenter":"Enough. We have already heard!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":402101,"lipSynch":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Tart","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":830200,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Dauphin Charles","textCenter":"You have truly done a magnificent job, La Pucelle."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20081.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":830300,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":830300}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"La Pucelle...@Why did I...forget about you?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Indeed."},{"chara":[{"id":830500}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"...We fought together with that maiden,"},{"chara":[{"id":830500}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"and were saved by her many times..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":830300}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameCenter":"Perenelle & Nicolas","textCenter":"...!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":402901},{"effect":"fadeout","id":831700}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":400,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":830300,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Do you remember now?"},{"chara":[{"id":830300},{"id":831303,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Ah..."},{"chara":[{"id":830300}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"She always stood at the forefront on the battlefield,@encouraging us."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":830300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"But outside of battles, she was friendly,@modest...a truly kind girl."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51158_tower_tart2/51158_kagome_magical_pencil.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Um... Can you tell me more about your story?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51158_tower_tart2/51158_kagome_magical_pencil.png","visible":"hide"}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":830300,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1.0},{"chara":[{"id":830300}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"...Hahaha, yeah, there were such moments.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.0},{"chara":[{"id":830500}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"His tent overflowed with gifts for La Pucelle."},{"chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Yeah! Wherever she went, she was popular."},{"chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"She had such an unpretentious and down-to-earth@personality because she was a simple village girl."},{"chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Even before her name became known throughout@France,"},{"chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"she was already incredibly popular everywhere she@went."},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"bg":"bg_adv_31122.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":402101,"motion":100,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":801000}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"La Pucelle!","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":801000}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I've brought you eggs, freshly laid this morning."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801000,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Bon appétit!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801400,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402101,"motion":201}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Are you taking care of yourself, young lady?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":801200,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402101,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"La Pucelle! Play with us again sometime! "},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":402101},{"effect":"fadeout","id":801200}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_31122.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402201,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Liz","textCenter":"She's been drawing a crowd every day lately...@She sure is popular."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20081.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":830300,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":830300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"...@...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Yes... La Pucelle was undoubtedly our comrade."},{"chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Our closest friend...and we forgot about her..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":830300}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"[chara:831303:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]But, thank you for remembering her."},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830400,"lipSynch":0,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"..."},{"bgm":"bgm03_story06","chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"You really look so much like her...@Jeanne La Pucelle."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"Yeah, despite being much younger,@you're the spitting image of her."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810000,"pos":1,"posY":80},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"...To those who have seen her up close,@she looks the same, huh?"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameCenter":"Qube","textCenter":"By the way, Kagome Satori,@have you finished recording?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Ah...yes! I just finished writing."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":831303},{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001},{"effect":"fadeout","id":810000}],"flashEffect":"explosion","se":"3205_charm","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402901,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"[chara:402901:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]...?!"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"They disappeared...?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":831700},{"effect":"fadeout","id":402901}],"flashEffect":"explosion","se":"3205_charm","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830400,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"What's going on...?"},{"chara":[{"id":830400}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"All four of them are gone?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
